            <title>[LU-19917] MGS replica imperative recovery support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19917</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;. update MGS replica nidtbl upon MGC notify&lt;br/&gt;
. enqueue IR on OSTs to support MGS replica on OST, though IR won&apos;t&lt;br/&gt;
  take effect, but it will notify MGS replica on the node&lt;br/&gt;
. update test script zconf_mount() to use MGS replicas for client&lt;br/&gt;
  mount, with this change, MDTs/OSTs use MGS0, while clients use&lt;br/&gt;
  MGS replicas, and the replica list is shuffled to distribute&lt;br/&gt;
  client connections among all MGS replicas&lt;/p&gt;</description>
